terraform init
terraform fmt    - formatting in all of your configuration files  
terraform validate   - Validate your configuration
terraform apply   - Apply the configuration 
terraform show   - Inspect the current state
terraform state list    -  list of the resources in your project's state.
terraform destroy   - terminates resources managed by your Terraform project.

terraform apply -var "instance_name=YetAnotherName"  - for providing another name to instance 
terraform output  - Terraform prints output values to the screen when you apply your configuration.



terraform apply -auto-approve






mkdir learn-terraform-docker-container
